    I - input symbol type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<VPDSym<I>>, Collection<VPDSym<I>>, Comparator<VPDSym<I>>, IntFunction<VPDSym<I>>, ToIntFunction<VPDSym<I>>, List<VPDSym<I>>, ArrayWritable<VPDSym<I>>, Alphabet<VPDSym<I>>, VPDAlphabet<VPDSym<I>>

    public class GrowingVPDAlphabet<I>
extends AbstractVPDAlphabet<VPDSym<I>>
    A VPDAlphabet implementation that allows to add new symbols after its construction. Wraps input symbols in a VPDSym instance to allow faster mappings from symbols to indexes.
    Author:
    Malte Isberner
